{"tid":629208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罵警被捕　女子上訴得直","createTime":"2018-04-14T13:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T13:42:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4feef4e66656f5e0b49db959da6fe857244ac450","tid":629208,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361125?_ga=2.136981168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361125%3F_ga%3D2.136981168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=B00LNoCgMr4boGkBCs%2BB%2BfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=69aaf4ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361125%3F_ga%3D2.136981168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=c8cecab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361125?_ga=2.136981168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n罵警被捕　女子上訴得直<br />\n<br />\n2.4K<br />\n法庭<br />\n <br />\n高等法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】夜歸女子遭街上雜物阻擋家門，報警求助，但不滿到場警員未能即時解決問題，高聲指摘警員。<br />\n<br />\n警員見狀即表示懷疑她藏毒，當街搜身卻未有發現，遂以阻差辦公罪名拘捕她，最終控以「醉酒及行為不檢」罪，審訊後罪成罰款2,000元。<br />\n<br />\n女子不服上訴，庭上披露急症室醫生沒記錄她醉酒或有酒氣，高院昨指女子行為確不檢，但未能證明她醉酒，裁定上訴得直。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指醉酒　官：無證據<br />\n<br />\n上訴人葉罕芬被控於去年2月21日凌晨在深水埗黃竹街犯案。控方指當日上址有公司因漏水而將文件雜物放門外，引來拾荒者，東主與拾荒者爭執，葉見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n惟葉對到場警員大吵大鬧講粗口，她飲啤酒及表現激動，身上有酒氣。<br />\n<br />\n辯方則表示葉當時正欲回家，但是大門被阻，故報警，警員到場反出言侮辱及講粗口指她多事，又揶揄指她住不起該處。<br />\n<br />\n她其後向警員跟進事件，並投訴現場有人吸煙恐惹火災，警員卻指她神志不清，思疑她吸毒，當街搜身。<br />\n<br />\n她不忿稱會追究，警員聞言以「阻差辦公」罪拘捕她。她否認飲酒，急症室醫生亦沒相關紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n法官指葉深夜在公眾地方用粗言穢語大聲責罵警員，確是行為不檢，惟控方未能證明她醉酒，因沒證人指出她有常見的醉酒舉止如胡言亂語、步履不穩或目光渙散等。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCMA469/17<br />\n■記者楊家樂"},{"pid":"1e0edfff870ef19008993c4452fbca55b21e93be","tid":629208,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:27:58.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"002c24745a347045d5e18d35d44dab4df81ba161","tid":629208,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:42:45.000Z","msg":"行為不檢呢條戇尻罪真係萬能key 只要個差佬唔妥你告你行為不檢就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}